<L>__{interior henry's apartment day}
<A>__{moments later. the door is wrenched open and henry is hit square in the jaw by a decade of dank airless gloom. he coughs. entering, he finds a few old wooden chairs littering the main room. he inspects the old wood stove, then takes a chair and smashes it. he tosses the wood in the stove. simon looks on, amazed. henry lights a fire with unusually quick results, then stands back and looks at simon.}
